## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-297">Web 組件控制集不會實作任何預設行為<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-297">The Web Parts control set does not implement any default behavior for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-298">不過，屬性會提供，因此您可以將任意字串值指派給自訂<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>控制; 屬性來檢查<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager>期間控制其<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.AuthorizeWebPart>事件，以判斷控制項是否可以加入頁面.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-298">However, the property is provided so that you can assign an arbitrary string value to a custom <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> control; this property can be checked by the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager> control during its <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.AuthorizeWebPart> event to determine whether the control can be added to the page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-299">在某些情況下，<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>名稱，因此，如果使用者同時隸屬於特定的角色，而且如果屬性可能會與 ASP.NET 角色管理員功能，使用的字串值<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>屬性符合開發人員，設定特定條件，則可以新增控制項。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-299">In some cases, the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property might be used with the ASP.NET role manager feature, so that if a user is in a certain role, and if the string value of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property meets certain conditions set by the developer, then the control can be added.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-300">這種方法可讓開發人員建立的角色和其他授權的準則，其所指定的組合為基礎的自訂檢視。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-300">This approach allows developers to create custom views of a page based on a combination of roles and other authorization criteria that they specify.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-301">這個屬性無法由佈景主題或樣式表主題設定。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-301">This property cannot be set by themes or style sheet themes.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-302">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> 並[ASP.NET 佈景主題和面板](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-302">For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.ThemeableAttribute> and [ASP.NET Themes and Skins](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/5df3ebbd-d46c-4502-9406-02f9df4ef2c3).</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-303">個人化範圍，這個屬性會設定為<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared>而且只能由授權的使用者可以修改。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-303">The personalization scope of this property is set to <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizationScope.Shared> and can be modified only by authorized users.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-304">如需詳細資訊，請參閱 <<c0> <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute> 並[Web 組件個人化概觀](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7dc34f74-52aa-4082-b98d-2bcf9e07e320)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-304">For more information, see <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.PersonalizableAttribute> and [Web Parts Personalization Overview](https://msdn.microsoft.com/library/7dc34f74-52aa-4082-b98d-2bcf9e07e320).</span></span>  
  
   
  
## Examples  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-305">下列程式碼範例示範使用<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>屬性。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-305">The following code example demonstrates the use of the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-306">它示範如何設定自訂方法的處理常式<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.AuthorizeWebPart>事件，以便處理常式可以提供自訂的篩選程式碼，如<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnAuthorizeWebPart%2A>方法。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-306">It shows how to set a custom method handler for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.AuthorizeWebPart> event, so that the handler can provide custom filtering code for the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPartManager.OnAuthorizeWebPart%2A> method.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-307">此範例中會提供篩選的案例和授權的網頁開發人員的典型方式<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart>控制項加入至頁面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-307">This example would be a typical way for a page developer to provide a filtering scenario and authorization of <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart> controls to be added to a page.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="925bf-308">在網頁程式碼中，注意`<asp:webpartmanager>`項目具有`OnAuthorizeWebPart`屬性指派給它的事件處理常式的名稱。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-308">In the Web page code, notice that the `<asp:webpartmanager>` element has the `OnAuthorizeWebPart` attribute with the name of the event handler assigned to it.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-309">這個方法會檢查頁面上的控制項是否有其<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>屬性值設定為`admin`，然後如果是的話，傳回`true`，這表示將會獲得授權並新增至頁面。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-309">This method checks whether the controls on the page have their <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property value set to `admin`, and if so, returns `true`, which means that they will be authorized and added to the page.</span></span>  
  
> [!NOTE]
>  <span data-ttu-id="925bf-310">請注意，控制項沒有任何值，指派給<xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A>屬性會加入，因為它們假設為無法篩選案例的一部分。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-310">Note that controls that do not have any value assigned to the <xref:System.Web.UI.WebControls.WebParts.WebPart.AuthorizationFilter%2A> property are added as well, because they are assumed not to be part of a filtering scenario.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="925bf-311">這會是篩選案例中常見的方法： 某些控制項進行篩選，和其他人不會因為它們都假設為可供所有使用者。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="925bf-311">This would be a common approach in a filtering scenario: some controls would be filtered, and others would not be, because they are presumed to be available for all users.</span></span>  
  
